---
const notes = [
  ['Field notes', 'What customers mean when they say “just make it simple.”'],
  ['A useful landing page', 'The answer is often less copy, not more copy.'],
  ['Operating manual', 'A small team needs decisions it can repeat.'],
];
---
<html lang="en"><head><title>Fieldwork — editorial starter</title><style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono&family=Libre+Baskerville:wght@400;700&display=swap');*{box-sizing:border-box}body{margin:0;background:#fffdf5;color:#1e2820;font-family:'Libre Baskerville',serif}.wrap{max-width:960px;margin:auto;padding:28px}header{border-bottom:1px solid #1e2820;padding-bottom:22px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font:12px 'DM Mono'}h1{max-width:720px;font-size:clamp(45px,8vw,88px);line-height:1.04;letter-spacing:-4px;margin:100px 0 40px}.intro{font-size:19px;line-height:1.6;max-width:580px}.list{margin-top:75px;border-top:1px solid #1e2820}.post{display:grid;grid-template-columns:180px 1fr;gap:20px;padding:26px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1e2820}.post span{font:11px 'DM Mono';text-transform:uppercase}.post h2{font-size:25px;margin:0 0 10px}.post p{margin:0;line-height:1.55}@media(max-width:600px){h1{letter-spacing:-2px;margin-top:70px}.post{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:8px}}</style></head><body><main class="wrap"><header><b>FIELDWORK</b><span>Journal / 001</span></header><h1>Ideas from the work, not around it.</h1><p class="intro">A minimal editorial site for an agency publication, founder blog, documentation hub, or SEO-led content library.</p><section class="list">{notes.map(([tag, title]) => <article class="post"><span>{tag}</span><div><h2>{title}</h2><p>Read the thinking behind better products, sharper messages, and calmer systems.</p></div></article>)}</section></main></body></html>
